**NRE (Non-Resident External) FDs** allow NRIs to deposit foreign earnings in India in Indian rupees. The interest earned on NRE FDs is completely exempt from Indian income tax and freely repatriable to any country. Current NRE FD rates range from 6.5% to 8% p.a. depending on the bank and tenure.
